The marketing manager will drive the innovation and development of appealing marketing concepts to promote Xtremax as an organisation and our products.
Job Responsibilities:

  Conceptualize marketing campaign themes, approaches and targets to promote awareness of new products and services of Xtremax
  Evaluate performance of existing and new marketing communication strategies based on programme targets to identify areas of improvement
  Plan, develop and implement effective marketing communications and product positioning strategies for Xtremax's products and services to help achieve sales target and profitability
  Determine growth opportunities across target segments and develop initiatives to drive engagement with them
  Oversee and manage the development and curation of offline and digital content, events and campaigns for marketing communication strategies
  Review functionalities of digital marketing platforms to improve the quality and type of data obtained
  Analyse market segments to identify and develop new target customers
  Develop relationships with suitable partners to leverage partner network and reach to support marketing objectives
  Review the effectiveness of existing marketing events and develop measures to further improve them

Job Requirements:

  Minimum 5-7 years of relevant experience in marketing field
  Ability to work in a fast-paced, dynamic and digitally-centric environment
  Innovative, energetic, collaborative and highly adaptable team leader
  Have strong interpersonal skills and a high level of initiative
  Excellent written and verbal communication skills
